  randomFlavorTableTitle: A HIDDEN BLADE
  randomFlavorTableRows:
  - '1 Twisted ebony handle Hidden within your

    shadow'
  - '2 Feather motif Can be thrown any

    distance'
  - '3 Tapered slicer +2d10 vs somebody

    who trusts you'
  - 4 Fang-like dagger Appears as a twig
  - 5 Long wavy blade Splits into two blades
  - "6 Etched bone Harmless to you\nKNIGHTED BY...\nThe Needle Seer\nVIG 8, CLA 14,
    SPI 6, 4 GD\n\u2022 Tall and slender, festooned with blades.\n\u2022 Pulls open
    small tears in reality, showing\nwhat could have been but is now\nimpossible.\n\u2022
    Wants to make other people feel bad, but\ngrudgingly does their duty to the Realm."
